data.description: Location, Location, Location!  Gorgeous Remodeled Home with an ADU!  located in the very desirable North Claremont area walking distance from the High School, to parks, colleges and shopping.  This Beautiful home features 5 bedrooms, 2.5 baths with a 11,356 Sq Ft lot.  The home was remodeled in 2021, over $125,000 was spent remodeling the kitchen and home * Large open kitchen with dozens of cabinets for ample storage * All bedrooms have ceiling fans * recessed lights throughout * New flooring * New energy efficient windows and new sliding glass doors to access the gorgeous ranch style back yard * It has a paid-for 48 solar panel system that provides enough power to cover the entire electrical bill * The home has a one year old dual efficient air conditioning system * The front and back yard were landscaped last year with a drip system to conserve water and maintain the beauty of the home * The back yard has many fruit trees and a gorgeous covered patio ideal for entertaining * Wide Driveway for extra vehicles *  The ADU is a permitted studio that was completed last year with a full bath, washer and dryer * It provides one parking space for the tenant who is on a month-to-month rental agreement
